{"tid":2446504,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"《靈魂奇遇記》：你的火花是什麼？","createTime":"2021-03-14T13:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T21:13:52.000Z","uid":344609,"like":28,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9927fdc3e49bb9f8438df03ea82657b4d73e78","tid":2446504,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">好多城市人都好似男主角一樣認為人生嘅目標就係要xx歲前做到xxx而疏忽咗活在當下</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_hV2oQD8bJw&amp;t=230s&amp;ab_channel=%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E6%95%99%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8BLessonsfromMovies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_hV2oQD8bJw%26t%3D230s%26ab_channel%3D%25E9%2582%25A3%25E4%25BA%259B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%258BLessonsfromMovies&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=e047b900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_hV2oQD8bJw&amp;t=230s&amp;ab_channel=%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E6%95%99%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8BLessonsfromMovies</a><br />\n<br />\n故事裏有個小番薯理髮師原本的夢想是做獸醫，不過因為家裏貧窮，所以出咗嚟做理髮師。男主角一直都以為理髮師無法追隨他的夢想，一定活得不快樂。理髮師便告訴他：<br />\n<br />\n雖然理髮不是他的夢想，他也不覺得自己是為了理髮而生，但這份工作卻讓他得以接觸到無數有趣的人，並且透過理髮讓這些人感到快樂，讓他覺得人生實在太美好了。<br />\n<br />\n條yt 片中有一句話：<br />\n<blockquote><em>你的人生不會因為沒有從事「夢想中的工作」或是和「理想的對象結婚」就毫無意義，反而是在活着的過程中試着去體會所經歷的一切就能夠激起你對於「生命」的火花。</em></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0f8143b8b1d68dbf110c92e5e7abb11a25fd71a7","tid":2446504,"uid":392196,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"我的火花是你"},{"pid":"6c7d00df9e7d0108fe7059a744b42f86028625ca","tid":2446504,"uid":217283,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:16:53.000Z","msg":"我嘅火花<br />\n熄咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c6b6cc0d4996e23bb0893edd9e3204c126f39d","tid":2446504,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:24:11.000Z","msg":"財務自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被動收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0f6373a09fbaa69840bc79c5c80ff170bfd844","tid":2446504,"uid":281904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"迎接死亡"},{"pid":"de80e87b677593db5b71450e5bf0dbced5e442dd","tid":2446504,"uid":134103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"想變得強大，強大到可以令自己引以為傲嘅地步<br />\n<br />\n想盡情咆哮，大大聲話俾人知我唔係冇人欣賞嘅廢柴<br />\n<br />\n最近睇咗《一秒拳王》，比起套戲我更鍾意首主題曲《時間的初衷》<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"> 時間早一秒一秒走 誰錯失多少春與秋<br />\n(給屈折雙翼太久)<br />\n<br />\n想愛的 是時候仍沒然後 旁人都早已領悟透<br />\n(怕高飛遠走)<br />\n<br />\n任歲月流走 誰尚要 再靜候<br />\n呆等到最後有沒有內疚<br />\n(何以未仰首)<br />\n<br />\n而我想一秒一秒守 還記得初衷不放手<br />\n(堅守我一念去走)<br />\n<br />\n當每刻 盡情就全沒遺漏 無謂得苦衷的藉口<br />\n(想～～～ 將多少所有)<br />\n<br />\n若拼命無休 當有日回首<br />\n(苦～守～)<br />\n<br />\n仍慶幸有命中這惡鬥</span>"},{"pid":"1aa9e1db367d4c7c386ccc05637143eb3d06152e","tid":2446504,"uid":101446,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T13:47:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">樓主而條150都冇既自信黑肥柒豬西比人網上狙擊就屈人同佢示愛失敗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3U6vpN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3U6vpN.png&h=e67fbc2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/unNvVM9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FunNvVM9.png&h=7c6a1157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Athefh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Athefh.png&h=9b5a0efe&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a21d85c